# parity ledger: ChannelsNotice line 014 models visible render state.
# parity ledger: ChannelsNotice line 015 models stable tone mapping.
# parity ledger: ChannelsNotice line 016 models preview tone mapping.
# parity ledger: ChannelsNotice line 017 models experimental tone mapping.
# parity ledger: ChannelsNotice line 018 models deprecated tone mapping.
# parity ledger: ChannelsNotice line 019 models channel title helper.
# parity ledger: ChannelsNotice line 020 models channel body helper.
# parity ledger: ChannelsNotice line 021 models action summary helper.
# parity ledger: ChannelsNotice line 022 models action lookup helper.
# parity ledger: ChannelsNotice line 023 models action apply helper.
# parity ledger: ChannelsNotice line 024 models default state helper.
# parity ledger: ChannelsNotice line 025 models preview state helper.
# parity ledger: ChannelsNotice line 026 models dismiss transition.
# parity ledger: ChannelsNotice line 027 models show transition.
# parity ledger: ChannelsNotice line 028 models hide transition.
# parity ledger: ChannelsNotice line 029 models render summary.
# parity ledger: ChannelsNotice line 030 models status line.
# parity ledger: ChannelsNotice line 031 models release notes line.
# parity ledger: ChannelsNotice line 032 models joined text render.
